CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 20, 1954, pg. 9, reads: "New Home Nursing Course - A six-week home nursing course given by the Red Cross and sponsored by Soho Community House at Wadsworth Hall started Tuesday, Nov. 16.  Some of those taking the course are, top photo: Nancy Jeffers, Charlotte Shelton, Margaret Woodley, Mittie Ellis, Wanda Coston, Betty Wilkes, Pauline Fariclough, Emma Hearst, Dorothy Malloy and Carrie Cox... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Red Cross home nursing class participants Nancy Jeffers, Charlotte Shelton, Margaret Woodley, Mittie Ellis, Wanda Coston, Betty Wilkes, Pauline Fariclough, Emma Hearst, Dorothy Malloy, and Carrie Cox gathered in Soho Community House, Wadsworth Hall
